The paper deals with recommender systems, which are often used in human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of latent factor models is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also deals with natural language processing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL).
